        C27 | Jobs Executive Appointmen­ts SATURDAY, SEPTEMBER 26, 2020 Executive Appointmen­ts Petroleum Authority of Brunei Darussalam is a statutory body to undertake the regulatory and monitoring of the upstream, midstream and downstream activities and operations, and act as custodian of petroleum data in Brunei Darussalam. MCC Singapore is inviting dedicated and motivated talents to join our team. Our newly awarded projects include Mandai Rainforest Park North & South Project and Short Street Hotel. We would like to invite a well-qualified, dynamic and experience­d profession­al to join Petroleum Authority as the Managing Director (MD). MANAGING DIRECTOR PROJECT
• Site Manager
• Project Engineer • Architectu­ral Coordinato­r • Structural Engineer/
Coordinato­r
